Definition: a course of reasoning aimed at demonstrating a truth or falsehood
Example: the methodical process of logical reasoning; I can't follow your line of reasoning
Synonyms: verb, communication, argue, logical_argument, argument, line_of_reasoning, line, reasoning, a, course, of, aimed, at, demonstrating, truth, or, falsehood, the, methodical, process, logical, I, can, t, follow, your
Category: noun.cognition
